	<h1 class="title">他拍了近年最好看的国产悬疑片《心迷宫》，想要告诉观众没有绝对的好与坏</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-19 17:07:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16274/medium/16274.jpg?1445247514" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


